madkit.message.hook.CGREvent

  • Packages that use CGREvent 
    Package Description
    madkit.message.hook
    Contains message classes useful for monitoring MaDKit kernel events.

    • Uses of CGREvent in madkit.message.hook

      Subclasses of CGREvent in madkit.message.hook 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  MessageEvent
      A message which is sent to agents that have requested a hook on HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.AGENT_STARTED or HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.AGENT_TERMINATED
      class  OrganizationEvent
      A message which is sent to agents that have requested a hook on HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.CREATE_GROUP, HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.REQUEST_ROLE, HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.LEAVE_GROUP, or HookMessage.AgentActionEvent.LEAVE_ROLE
